item.title: W600
item.description: W600-SDK Overview WizFi360 is based on the W600 chip which features ARM Cortex-M3 with 1MB on-chip flash and freeRTOS kernel. This page includes the software development kit (SDK) files, documents, and usage method. This SDK has integrated WizFi360 hardware driver (BSP), RTOS, TCP/IP protocol, Wi-Fi Protocol and other public function modules. Software SDK Official SDK from chip vendor Download link - WizFi360 Chip SDK (wm_sdk_w60x_g3.02.00_190729.zip) Software SDK User Manual Basic SDK User Manual V1.
